# External API Integrations

## Time and Astronomical Data
- Sunrise/Sunset API: https://sunrise-sunset.org/api
- Moon Phase API: https://api.farmsense.net/v1/moonphases/
- DST & Timezone API: https://worldtimeapi.org/

## Environmental Data
- Schumann Resonance: Scraped from HeartMath
- Solar Activity: NOAA API (https://services.swpc.noaa.gov/json/)

## API Usage Guidelines
1. Implement proper error handling for all API calls
2. Cache responses where appropriate
3. Implement rate limiting
4. Handle API downtime gracefully
5. Store API keys securely

## Data Storage
- Store processed data in MongoDB
- Implement data validation
- Set up proper indexing for queries
- Regular backup procedures

